:: A Doorway on Dean Street {"position":"700,550","size":"100,100"}
(set: $hadBreather to true)\
(set: $breatherReturns to $returns + 1)\
(set: $confidence to $confidence + 12)\
(if: $hadChippy is true)[(set: $sobriety to $sobriety + 5)](else:)[(set: $sobriety to $sobriety + 20)]\
The coast is clear so you spew up your guts with the tact of a bulimic starlette. Well done. You feel much better for that.

[[Back to Dean Street|Dean Street]]

