:: At the Corner of Dean Street and Greek Street {"position":"1200,400","size":"100,100"}
<!-- Ginger light -->
<div class="ginger-lamp-wrap">
<svg width="60" height="110" viewBox="0 0 60 110"><ellipse cx="30" cy="33" rx="40" ry="30" fill="rgba(200,100,5,0.10)"/><ellipse cx="30" cy="31" rx="24" ry="18" fill="rgba(220,130,10,0.18)"/><ellipse cx="30" cy="29" rx="13" ry="10" fill="rgba(255,190,60,0.22)"/><polygon points="27,2 30,0 33,2 32,7 28,7" fill="rgba(60,38,4,0.96)"/><path d="M13,7 Q30,4 47,7 L44,13 L16,13 Z" fill="rgba(60,38,4,0.96)"/><path d="M16,13 L44,13 L40,44 L20,44 Z" fill="rgba(130,75,8,0.45)" stroke="rgba(90,52,4,0.65)" stroke-width="1"/><path d="M19,15 L41,15 L37,42 L23,42 Z" fill="rgba(255,165,35,0.42)"/><ellipse cx="30" cy="29" rx="7" ry="10" fill="rgba(255,232,130,0.55)"/><ellipse cx="30" cy="27" rx="3" ry="4" fill="rgba(255,250,210,0.68)"/><rect x="22" y="44" width="16" height="6" rx="2.5" fill="rgba(60,38,4,0.96)"/><rect x="27" y="50" width="6" height="60" rx="2" fill="rgba(45,28,3,0.90)"/></svg>
</div>
<div class="ginger-scene">
<div class="ginger-light"></div>
A man, not much past twenty, stands under a ginger light. At first you think he must be a dilly boy. He wears a beret and paints his nails; he is epicene and crinoline, as if he might snap at any moment.

Then you clock him for a poet that you know. A poet called Red.

Like a tiger in the Taiga, moving strong and low through heavy blizzard, whose footprints fill as soon as they are made, what Red leaves of himself on the street is trackless at your shutter-speed; he is a bundle of scents and of the weightless bergs of ash he calves into the puddle at his feet, which, even when they should be extinguished, are, by some feeling wind, awakened to a transitory brightness.

You stand near for a while; he is somewhere far off, elsewhere.

[[Speak to him|You speak to the poet]]
</div>

:: Beaten [venue-cellar] {"position":"2200,1250","size":"100,100"}
<!-- Swinging bulb -->
<div class="cellar-bulb-wrap">
<svg width="48" height="90" viewBox="0 0 48 90"><!-- Wire from ceiling --><line x1="24" y1="0" x2="24" y2="30" stroke="#888878" stroke-width="1.4" opacity="0.75"/><!-- Socket cap --><rect x="17" y="28" width="14" height="10" rx="2.5"fill="rgba(80,78,65,0.9)" stroke="rgba(160,155,120,0.7)" stroke-width="1"/><!-- Socket ring detail --><rect x="19" y="36" width="10" height="3" rx="1"fill="none" stroke="rgba(150,145,110,0.55)" stroke-width="0.8"/><!-- Outer glow halo --><ellipse cx="24" cy="60" rx="20" ry="22"fill="rgba(255,245,160,0.12)"/><!-- Bulb body — pear shape, bright and solid --><path d="M24,38 C16,38 10,45 10,55 C10,67 16,78 24,78 C32,78 38,67 38,55 C38,45 32,38 24,38 Z"fill="rgba(255,252,210,0.95)" stroke="rgba(220,210,160,0.6)" stroke-width="0.8"/><!-- Inner warm core --><ellipse cx="24" cy="57" rx="9" ry="11"fill="rgba(255,240,120,0.55)"/><!-- Filament — W-shape --><path d="M18,60 L20,53 L24,58 L28,53 L30,60"fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,200,40,0.95)" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linejoin="round"/><!-- Neck base ring --><rect x="20" y="75" width="8" height="3" rx="1"fill="rgba(200,195,155,0.65)" stroke="none"/></svg>
</div>
<div class="cellar-scene">
<div class="cellar-light"></div>
(set: $wasBeaten to true)
Copper's short hook catches you and you're floored.

'I don't talk to liars,' he says.

He's about to finish what he started, when a voice calls from the staircase, 'Salvu! Leave it! He's alright.' It's John St. John. 'I know him. I don't like him but he's sound.'

St. John's face is legible only to you, who once knew him so well. He's amused at your straits, both pleased that you're in them, and miffed that it falls on him to rescue you, again.

(if: $metRed is true)[He leans close when he pulls you to your feet: 'Red told Copper you had money.']

(if: $knowsCopperWord)[Copper turns his back and before he does, he takes from his pocket a book of matches and gives them to John St. John, who gives them to you.

'Well,' says John. 'That went better than anyone expected.'
(set: $hasTrishaMatchbook to true)
[[Try Trisha's|Failure: Trisha's]]]
(else:)[[[He has something to tell you|St. John's Word]]]
</div>

:: St. John's Word [venue-cellar] {"position":"2200,1350","size":"100,100"}
<!-- Swinging bulb -->
<div class="cellar-bulb-wrap">
<svg width="48" height="90" viewBox="0 0 48 90"><!-- Wire from ceiling --><line x1="24" y1="0" x2="24" y2="30" stroke="#888878" stroke-width="1.4" opacity="0.75"/><!-- Socket cap --><rect x="17" y="28" width="14" height="10" rx="2.5"fill="rgba(80,78,65,0.9)" stroke="rgba(160,155,120,0.7)" stroke-width="1"/><!-- Socket ring detail --><rect x="19" y="36" width="10" height="3" rx="1"fill="none" stroke="rgba(150,145,110,0.55)" stroke-width="0.8"/><!-- Outer glow halo --><ellipse cx="24" cy="60" rx="20" ry="22"fill="rgba(255,245,160,0.12)"/><!-- Bulb body — pear shape, bright and solid --><path d="M24,38 C16,38 10,45 10,55 C10,67 16,78 24,78 C32,78 38,67 38,55 C38,45 32,38 24,38 Z"fill="rgba(255,252,210,0.95)" stroke="rgba(220,210,160,0.6)" stroke-width="0.8"/><!-- Inner warm core --><ellipse cx="24" cy="57" rx="9" ry="11"fill="rgba(255,240,120,0.55)"/><!-- Filament — W-shape --><path d="M18,60 L20,53 L24,58 L28,53 L30,60"fill="none" stroke="rgba(255,200,40,0.95)" stroke-width="1.4" stroke-linejoin="round"/><!-- Neck base ring --><rect x="20" y="75" width="8" height="3" rx="1"fill="rgba(200,195,155,0.65)" stroke="none"/></svg>
</div>
<div class="cellar-scene">
<div class="cellar-light"></div>
'Lackland's got a secret room. The word's //Valletta//,' says John as he marshals you out.

'Next time knock on the right door.'
(set: $confidence to $confidence - 18)
(if: $knowsCopperSecret is false)[(set: $knowsCopperSecret to true)

