<div class="cellar-scene">
<div class="cellar-light"></div>
(set: $confidence to $confidence + 12)

Salvu Copper's face droops under the heat of his internal furnace. 'So someone's looking after you? That's enough,' he says. Quiet Frankie lifts his hand without looking. Ashton Granger is happy you're alive. He presses a book of matches into your hand: 'Tell Trisha I sent you.'

(set: $hasTrishaMatchbook to true)
[[Try Trisha's|Failure: Trisha's]]
</div>
