(set: $sobriety to $sobriety + 20)\
Salvu Copper, who is proportioned brutally, opens the door and leans over the threshold, like a hawk might hang over its prey.

'Can I help you?' said Salvu.

<span class="guided-link">[['I'm a member.'|Approach Coppers Lair]]</span>
