'Bourbon,' says the guitarist. 'The one with the bird on the label. Tulip glass.'

'Moscow Mule,' says Moe de Alcousin. 'Fresh lime. Not bottled.'

'Scotch,' says the pianist. 'The Macallan. Neat.'

