(else:)[[[Return to the street|Dean Street]]]

:: Cow ride fail {"position":"900,1300","size":"100,100"}
(set: $confidence to $confidence - 8)\
The beast bucks. The cobblestones rush up.

You land badly, lie still a moment while the world readjusts itself around you. Someone steps over you without stopping. Typical Soho. The cow trots off without looking back.

[[Back to the street|Dean Street]]

