(set: $sobriety to $sobriety - 12)\
(set: $confidence to $confidence - 12)
You meet him, at the bar with a big scotch in one hand and a fag in the other.

He's getting a round in.

<p class="script-line"><span class="script-speaker">Him.</span> 'Pint of Guinness, double whisky, twice, and a gin and... no, you say it.'</p>
<p class="script-line"><span class="script-speaker">You.</span> '…and Bitter Lemon.'</p>

You move to his table and place your drink on a little vacant patch among his papers.

'I like books…'

<br>
[['… but I don't like all this drinking.'|None of us likes it!]]
[['… but I don't like poetry.'|None of us likes it!]]
(if: $hasCoin is true)[<script>if(window.coinGate)window.coinGate("'… but I don\u0027t like all this drinking.'","'… but I don\u0027t like poetry.'");</script>]
</div>

