0808" opacity="0.3"/><circle cx="-16" cy="1.5" r="1.2" fill="#1a0808" opacity="0.3"/><circle cx="16" cy="-1.5" r="1.2" fill="#1a0808" opacity="0.3"/><circle cx="16" cy="1.5" r="1.2" fill="#1a0808" opacity="0.3"/></g></svg>

<div class="phone-type" style="--d:0.3s;--t:1.0s">The phone rings behind the bar.</div>\
<div class="phone-type" style="--d:1.6s;--t:0.4s">It's Aoife.</div>\
<div class="phone-type phone-her" style="--d:2.4s;--t:1.4s">'Where are you?'</div>\
<div class="phone-type phone-you" style="--d:4.2s;--t:0.8s">'I'll be home soon,'</div>\
<div class="phone-type phone-her" style="--d:5.4s;--t:1.0s">'Just come back.'</div>\
<div class="phone-type" style="--d:6.8s;--t:0.6s">She hangs up.</div>
</div>

<div class="phone-scene lily-phone-scene" style="margin-top: 1.5em;">
<svg class="phone-rule lily-phone-rule" viewBox="0 0 300 55" width="100%" height="55" preserveAspectRatio="none"><defs><filter id="drBl2"><feGaussianBlur stdDeviation="5"/></filter><linearGradient id="drCd2" x1="0" x2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#4a3858" stop-opacity="0"/><stop offset="20%" stop-color="#6a4878" stop-opacity="0.42"/><stop offset="50%" stop-color="#7a5888" stop-opacity="0.55"/><stop offset="80%" stop-color="#6a4878" stop-opacity="0.42"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#4a3858" stop-opacity="0"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="drHd2" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#3a2048"/><stop offset="40%" stop-color="#5a3868"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#4a2858"/></linearGradient><radialGradient id="drGw2" cx="50%" cy="50%" r="55%"><stop offset="0%" stop-color="#b090c0" stop-opacity="0.10"/><stop offset="100%" stop-color="#b090c0" stop-opacity="0"/></radialGradient></defs><ellipse cx="140" cy="26" rx="52" ry="16" fill="#907098" opacity="0.05" filter="url(#drBl2)"/><ellipse cx="180" cy="30" rx="44" ry="14" fill="#806088" opacity="0.04" filter="url(#drBl2)"/><ellipse cx="150" cy="27" rx="95" ry="24" fill="url(#drGw2)"/><path d="M14 27 Q20 12 26 27 Q32 42 38 27 Q44 12 50 27 Q56 42 62 27 Q68 13 74 27 Q79 38 84 27 Q89 18 94 27 Q98 33 102 27 Q105 24 108 27" fill="none" stroke="url(#drCd2)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M192 27 Q195 24 198 27 Q202 33 206 27 Q211 18 216 27 Q221 38 226 27 Q232 13 238 27 Q244 42 250 27 Q256 12 262 27 Q268 42 274 27 Q280 12 286 27" fill="none" stroke="url(#drCd2)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/><circle cx="110" cy="27" r="2" fill="#5a3868" opacity="0.4"/><circle cx="190" cy="27" r="2" fill="#5a3868" opacity="0.4"/><g transform="translate(150,27) rotate(-8)"><path d="M-22 0 C-22,-8 -14,-9 -12,-5 C-10,-2 -6,-2 0,-2 C6,-2 10,-2 12,-5 C14,-9 22,-8 22,0 C22,8 14,9 12,5 C10,2 6,2 0,2 C-6,2 -10,2 -12,5 C-14,9 -22,8 -22,0 Z" fill="url(#drHd2)" opacity="0.55"/><circle cx="-16" cy="-1.5" r="1.2" fill="#1a0818" opacity="0.3"/><circle cx="-16" cy="1.5" r="1.2" fill="#1a0818" opacity="0.3"/><circle cx="16" cy="-1.5" r="1.2" fill="#1a0818" opacity="0.3"/><circle cx="16" cy="1.5" r="1.2" fill="#1a0818" opacity="0.3"/></g></svg>

<div class="phone-type lily-phone-narrate" style="--d:7.8s;--t:1.2s">It rings again. Immediately. A different ring. Longer. Older.</div>\
<div class="phone-type lily-phone-narrate" style="--d:9.4s;--t:0.4s">It's Lily.</div>\
<div class="phone-type lily-phone-her" style="--d:10.2s;--t:1.6s">'What was her name? I think she was next to me in my yoga class.'</div>\
<div class="phone-type lily-phone-you" style="--d:12.2s;--t:0.8s">'Isadora. And yes I was young and…'</div>\
<div class="phone-type lily-phone-her" style="--d:13.4s;--t:1.8s">'How different things might have been.'</div>\
<div class="phone-type lily-phone-you" style="--d:15.6s;--t:1.2s">'How changed they are.'</div>\
<div class="phone-type lily-phone-her" style="--d:17.2s;--t:0.8s">'Goodnight, and take life easy.'</div>\
<div class="phone-type lily-phone-narrate" style="--d:18.4s;--t:1.4s">'… as the grass grows on the weirs; but I was young and foolish.'</div>

