'Fresh blood,' says Jack Curtis. 'Fancy a game?'

'House rules,' says Johan Clogg. 'Winner plays the stranger.'

[[Challenge Jack Curtis|Challenge Jack Curtis]]
[[Challenge Johan Clogg|Challenge Johan Clogg]]
[[I'd rather just watch|Watch them play]]

:: Watch them play {"position":"1400,1300","size":"100,100"}
You watch them play.

'Lackland's sitting on something,' says Johan Clogg.

'Lackland's always sitting on something,' says Jack Curtis. 'It's what he does instead of standing for anything.'
(set: $confidence to $confidence + 4)
Jack Curtis tosses you a paddle. 'House rules.'

[[Take the paddle|Challenge Jack Curtis]]

